text: <@U026AP8CM|karen> has joined the channel

He also mentioned he sees inconsistencies where the Spanish version shows English sometimes and I'm figuring that's the same thing on the other android builds - that we just can't guarantee that will work every time if you're flipping back and forth between English and Spanish. I'll forward you the email.

unfortunately, that wasn't one of the things I tested
